<div id="review_677027247" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/677027247" />
    <a title="Kerri" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/10405670-kerri"><img alt="Kerri" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1493044953p2/10405670.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/677027247?book_show_action=true">Nov 10, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kerri" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kerri" href="/user/show/10405670-kerri">Kerri</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer677027247" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4295643046442954246">Oh man, there is so much in this series that I had forgotten! Things are growing, story lines are still being introduced. The characters grow and change and there are crazy worlds full of so much depth and life. <br/><br/><a class='jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction'>(view spoiler)</a><span class='spoilerContainer' style='display: none'>[<br/>I had forgotten the details of the different worlds. Giant bugs, the Kitchen, the dystopian Oz, Egypt, the flying world, Venice, the Patchwork world. <br/><br/>I had thought Dread to be Quan Li, but thought I was misremembering and leaned instead towards Florimel - I remembered it w</span></span>
  <span id="freeText4295643046442954246" style="display:none">Oh man, there is so much in this series that I had forgotten! Things are growing, story lines are still being introduced. The characters grow and change and there are crazy worlds full of so much depth and life. <br /><br /><a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[<br />I had forgotten the details of the different worlds. Giant bugs, the Kitchen, the dystopian Oz, Egypt, the flying world, Venice, the Patchwork world. <br /><br />I had thought Dread to be Quan Li, but thought I was misremembering and leaned instead towards Florimel - I remembered it was not Sweet William but one of the women. Before restarting the series, I hadn't remembered any of the group but !Xabbu, Renie, Orlando, and Fredericks/Sam, but faint memories trickled back.<br /><br />I had remembered the boy named Cho-Cho showed up again somehow when he helped Christabel cut the fence, but I didn't remember that he got caught inside the compound and joined up with Mr. Sellars. <br /> <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span></span>
  <a data-text-id="4295643046442954246" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

